title: Chuck S02E12 (2-D) from NBC.com (FLV format)
description:
This is the 2D version!

The quality is poor, but this is exactly what NBC is streaming on their site. I captured this using Replay Media Catcher, which records the exact digital stream. It is not a screen capture, but a digital stream recording. For some reason, it looks better on NBC's site than it does in my favorite video player (Gom Player), so I suspect the flash player on the site is using extra filters to hide the blockiness.
